git init          Is folder ko Git repository bana do

git status        Git tumhein batata hai: Kaunsi files hain,Kya tracked hai,Kya change hua ha

git .add          Local code ko Git ke under lao   . means sab files

git commit -m "first"  -m for message Is time par project ki condition save kar lo

git remote add origin https://github.com/Basitkhan900/E-commrace-1.git  for first time upload code on github repo with name

git push origin main      for  push code wit branch name


WHEN WE UPDATE CODE
git add .
git commit -m "update"
git push origin main






Formula for git
First time:
git init
git add .
git commit
git remote
git push

Next time:
git add
git commit
git push

Agar kisi or kha code run karna ho github kha
Friend tumhein GitHub repo ka link dega, jaisa  eg:- https://github.com/username/project-name
then open gitbash
git clone https://github.com/username/project-name.git          clone means git clone = online repo ko apne computer par copy karna
cd project-name  matlab jo project name ho wo likengy
npm install
npm run dev  copy link paste into browser

